metadata.name: Mushroom Queen
metadata.description:
A walking, ruling, representation of life and nature itself.

Owning this NFT grants you access to the Mushroom Queen 3d printable model files. These are for personal use only but if you want to sell 3d prints of them and models of mine that you own, you may obtain a commercial license here: https://www.patreon.com/monsterite

My NFTs are the real deal. You don't just obtain a cool piece of artwork, but the product behind it as well.
